<item>
            <title>[PIG-650] pig should look for and use the pig specific &apos;pig-cluster-hadoop-site.xml&apos; in the non HOD case just like it does in the HOD case</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-650</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently users can create a pig-cluster-hadoop-site.xml with pig specific overrides for hadoop properties for use on the cluster. This file is searched for in the classpath and used in the HOD case but not in the non HOD case. We should also do the same in the non HOD case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
